title: Ashley Braband
description: The plan was to wait until we were "ready" to record this episode. Fate intervened, and in hindsight it's hilarious that I thought one day we'd both wake up like, "ok I'm ready!" Our best friend Ashley Braband updates us on where she's at and how she's doing. It's very relatable and, as always, I hope it helps.
